{"tid":2247736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文字獄｜上海老牌牛奶公司廣告「請給我光明」 被指損國家尊嚴洩密罰35萬元","createTime":"2020-10-18T05:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T06:21:14.000Z","uid":271829,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"851bf43db35bb633dd07497e5587ce103688e9e0","tid":2247736,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n中國大興文字獄，就連老牌奶類製品廠上海「光明乳業」，亦疑因一句廣告宣傳句語：「請給我光明」而中招。據內地媒體報道，國家企業信用信息公示系統顯示，光明乳業因發佈廣告，觸犯「損害國家的尊嚴或利益、洩露國家秘密」法規，被上海當局罰款30萬元人民幣 （34.7萬港元）。有網民直指，光明乳業的「請給我光明」廣告語，「是在影射我們太黑暗了」；更有網民引述聖經，指「魔鬼是黑暗，最怕光」，所以「請給我光明」，根本是在暗諷在中共是魔鬼，這分明是在洩露國家機密，豈有不被清算之理！？<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201018/PJDBWEPQJFGV3KXEIJM2KKJHQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201018%2FPJDBWEPQJFGV3KXEIJM2KKJHQE%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPRQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=22a46b6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201018%2FPJDBWEPQJFGV3KXEIJM2KKJHQE%2F&h=bf0d9284\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201018/PJDBWEPQJFGV3KXEIJM2KKJHQE/</a>"},{"pid":"ea3168ea7dec869987a97a16b07e6b6cb47772e1","tid":2247736,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁仆街"},{"pid":"991d2d542be39754f0b50ec138c73663d5a5d054","tid":2247736,"uid":140309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"加速師從來唔會令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63b3bef41bfb9aabbf511d2ff481de169e648ca","tid":2247736,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"賣燈的都應該有罪"},{"pid":"525729bafba2846528fd4490ec7773cbdae5e406","tid":2247736,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！<br />\n成日捕風捉影"},{"pid":"